title: iPhone SE 3 now available to pre-order: 5G, A15 Bionic, Touch ID, and more
content:
Apple’s new third-generation iPhone SE is officially available to pre-order. After being announced during the “Peek Performance” special event this week, the iPhone SE 3 is now available to purchase via the Apple Store Online. The first pre-orders are slated to arrive in one week, on March 18.
